05/08/2003
ANKARA, Turkey -- UN Special Representative for Iraq Sergio de Mello met with Turkish Foreign Minister Abdullah Gul in Ankara Monday (4 August). The two discussed the political and diplomatic role that Turkey could play in the reconstruction of Iraq. Mello expressed the hope that Turkey would participate in the international conference on reconstruction scheduled for October. (Hurriyet, Milliyet - 05/08/03; Anadolu Agency, TRT 2 - 04/08/03)
